name: Cutesy The Bear
overview: Guide Cutesy the bear through 10 levels in the garden eliminate the baddies that threaten it in this colorful platformer by J. Monday from 1991. Bump the baddies from below and kick them off the platform remove them from the garden patch. Collect the snacks before clearing the last baddie gives a bonus snack screen! Each level is timed, so don't waste a precious second.
